要提供公共領域嘅廣東話句子、審查句子嘅正確性；幫句子錄音；同咪檢驗錄音喺咪同句子相符。計畫收集到嘅數據同豐富，就可以整到更準確嘅語音，甚至變成引擎，令廣東話語音辨識應用帶黎更好嘅效果。<br />\n<br />\n幫手撳呢度：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://voice.mozilla.org/zh-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvoice.mozilla.org%2Fzh-HK&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=874b05fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://voice.mozilla.org/zh-HK</a><br />\n<br />\n Source: <a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/3790?fbclid=IwAR3lNATGdoFUcxKli15D5DgCWS952xUkDDGhHXFCcwsHHtEIEEHQE7OMIew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F3790%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3lNATGdoFUcxKli15D5DgCWS952xUkDDGhHXFCcwsHHtEIEEHQE7OMIew&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=7e167a29\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/3790?fbclid=IwAR3lNATGdoFUcxKli15D5DgCWS952xUkDDGhHXFCcwsHHtEIEEHQE7OMIew</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"一吹雞即刻夠數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c088092bad4558a001281fdd2dd9fbae2a121a","tid":2048420,"uid":80303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:36:41.000Z","msg":"ching 食住依家香港本土個勢<br />\n唔夠數就大力吹雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aed9676806b4487a6e0ff0897b039b93c23820b","tid":2048420,"uid":83874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a1c088092bad4558a001281fdd2dd9fbae2a121a","tid":2048420,"uid":80303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:36:41.000Z","msg":"ching 食住依家香港本土個勢<br />\n唔夠數就大力吹雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif